reviewText: Billy Fury-His Wondrous Story is a fantastic DVD about Billy Fury. Showing his life and musical history, it was released in 2007. Tells the truth behind the pop star image, and his health problems. With 29 hit singles in England , he was one of the top singers in the 1960's. Billy didn't make a big impact in the United States, but he became a big star in England. Fans of Billy Fury will like this the most.
